{'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'A nice cozy studio for a family or a couple who needs to rest near the pool and our magnificient garden. The children love to be near the pool and the adults loves to rest reading a book or playing chess.
Come to enjoy your vacations to our hospitable mansion

a very nice cozy studio, with view to the pool and the garden, with no neighbor 
surrounded by olive trees.

you will need car, motobike in order to get to the beach or to a restaurant.
if you like walking the distance from the beach or the taverna or mini market is about a kilometer', 'houseRules': '.Cleaning is done daily from 10:00 am to 2:00 pm.
.In case you do not want cleaning, please let us know.
.The pool is open from 8:00 am to 10:00 pm.
.After 23:00 pm, the doors are locked for security reasons and you unlock on your return with your own key.
.If you want us to wash your clothes, put them in the bags we provide and give them to us. sectionedDescription:
{'access': 'Перед апартаментами есть небольшой дворик с собственным входом, где могут играть маленькие дети! sectionedDescription:
{'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'This apartment village consists of 15 self-contained studios and apartments with their own fully equipped kitchen and bathroom. There are :
*  studios for 2 guests 
*  apartments with two bedrooms (Max 4 guests)
*  one Maisonette with 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms (max 8 + 2 guests)
The apartment village is on a low hill overlooking the Ionian Sea from every point of it. On walking distance, there are cosy taverns and restaurants as well as bars. 
ONLINE RATES ARE ONLY FOR ONE APARTMENT (4 guests)

The apartment village is spread in two pairs of buildings. One close to the pool and the other on a more private distance.
They are located near Acharavi-Corfu, which is known as Greece’s ‘Emerald Island’.  The apartment village is on a low hill overlooking the Ionian Sea from every point of it. That is a peaceful rural setting, at the start of an oak tree forest surrounded by nature with a fantastic sunset view. Guests are in a private and peaceful environment within walking distance from a virgin, sandy beach with shallow waters. On walking distance again there are also traditional taverns and restaurants as well as bars. And for those seeking something more active, there is Acharavi, the big resort of the area, just 1,5 km away.
 The apartment village offers a strategic position on the northern part of the island from where it is easy to explore the North East up to the North West some of the best destinations and beaches on the island.

24/7

Almiros, one of the most beautiful and virgin areas of Corfu, is situated on the north part of Corfu near the town of Acharavi, at the foot of mount Pantokratoras (914 m.) and just opposite the Albanian mountain range. Almiros Beach is almost 2 km. long and is extended from Acharavi to the picturesque lake “Antinioti”.
The beach has obtained the European Blue Flag. It is a long, beautiful sandy beach, with clear water and unspoiled scenery which remains as it was years ago. Nearby Almiros, there are many beautiful and peaceful bays for people who like swimming on small bays, away from noisy and crowded beaches. Almiros is in no way a resort as there are just six Tavernas servicing good quality food at good prices with very friendly manners.

The apartment village is 800 meters from the beach of Almiros, 100 meters from the Acharavi-Kassiopi main road and 300 from the public bus station. Acharavi is 2 km away.
There is a large parking area.

The family Maisonette is not for rent in July and August, as it is kept for private use. 

LISTED RATES ARE PER UNIT FOR LOFT MAISONETTES WITH 2 BEDROOMS AND 4 GUESTS CAPACITY. sectionedDescription:
{'authorType': 'human', 'description': "Offering garden views, Villa Fabio in Ksamil offers accommodations, a bar, a shared lounge, a garden and a terrace.

Accommodations is fitted with air conditioning and features a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a fully equipped kitchen with a dining area, and a private bathroom. A balcony with city views is offered in all units.

sectionedDescription:
{'authorType': 'human', 'description': "Α holiday complex of 5,385m2 and is located in the northern part of Corfu Island, in the centre ofAcharavi, one of Corfu’s most popular tourist resorts. Our holiday studios and apartments are conveniently located less than five minutes walk from the beach, shops and restaurants of the village of Acharavi and 38km from the Town of Corfu.
Corfu island is considered one of the prime vacation spots world-wide, attracting thousands of visitors every year and is distinguished by both traditional Greek and European characteristics, which have influenced Corfu's physical appearance and culture as well as the personality of the inhabitants. The island is verdant and has many lovely beaches ideal for swimming and sunbathing, while several areas offer magnificent sunset views.
Our sea side studios and apartments consist of five independent buildings that are either two or three storey high and in total they cover 27% of the total estate surface facilitating the comforts of a stress free and economic holiday in Corfu, providing a home atmosphere away from home. The remaining 73% of the estate surface is covered in vegetation, with lawns and beautifully shaped gardens, ideal for those seeking tranquility and relaxation in one of the prime vacation resorts world-wide, attracting thousands of visitors every year.
Except the ample room, the light and attractive low buildings and the relaxing atmosphere, our sea side studios and apartments in Acharavi also include a snack bar along with a full range of other amenities such as an Olympic size swimming pool, a children’s pool, a pool bar, and other facilities provide the convenience and comfort essential to relaxing in one of the top holiday resorts in Corfu.", 'locale': 'en', 'localizedLanguageName': 'English', 'name': 'One bedroom Apts in Arachavi', 'space': "Α holiday complex of 5,385m2 and is located in the northern part of Corfu Island, in the centre ofAcharavi, one of Corfu’s most popular tourist resorts. sectionedDescription:
{'access': 'We have a bar, restaurant, sun terrace, Free WIFI,  Free sunbeds and Sun umbrellas on the beach,  Fresh sheets and towels and beach bar .', 'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'Panoramic seaview Be&Breakfast room for 3, situated near bars, tavernas and shops at Agios Gordios, The beach is  5 minutes walk  away on foot,
comfortable room allowing you to enjoy the beautiful Agios Gordios beach and its crystal clear water. 
Room has 3 single beds, a seaview balcony with breathtaking  views,  private shower & toilette, fridge, kettel .
Free Wi-fi and a huge sun deck that over looks the water . We can arrange airport transfer at all hours. just give us arrival details please

We are located 38O meters from the beach on the hill, overlooking the sea. we are family owned hotel and we offer private sea view en-suite rooms. 
We are located 5 minutes walk  from the sandy beach of Agios Gordios. We have free WiFi in the public areas , like reception and lobby and our beach bar, also free parking and A/C sea view rooms
Our prices online includes: 
 * sea view en suite  private  room 
 *Free sunbeds & Sun chairs on the beach
 *Free WIFI 
*Free luggage room
*Taxes included in the price.

You can also rent cars,  bikes , scooters, quads.
We can also arrange pick up on arrival.  
We are only  3 minutes from the Agios Gordios village center where shops, bars, restaurants, local tavern's, medical center and bus stop.

Schedule our activities according to your preferences!

ACTIVITIES AND EXCURSIONS
1) DAILY Quad/4 Wheeler island Safaris (weather permitting)
2) Sea Kayak Tour & rentals (weather permitting)
4) Hiking, walking, and trekking (trails to nearby villages of Sinarades, Kato Garouna, Pavliana, and the unique fishing village of Pentati)
5) Horseback riding
6) Tours of Old Corfu Town and the island
7) Day trips to Aqualand Waterpark and other nearby attractions of your choice
8) Day trips to Albania

We have a bar, restaurant, sun terrace, Free WIFI,  Free sunbeds and Sun umbrellas on the beach,  Fresh sheets and towels and beach bar .

We and our staff like  to interact with our guests as much as possible and we are happy to assist you with anything you need.

Agios Gordios is a hidden gem on the south west coast of Corfu. The village itself is friendly and the views will take your breath away. Surrounded by spectacular olive-clad mountains, Agios Gordios and its sandy bay offers the perfect place for a quiet Corfu beach holiday. Safe for families and quiet for romantic couples, it's the kind of place that you want to keep YOUR secret! You can't help but be impressed by the view that greets you the first time you go down to the beach front. You get to the beach via the main street which runs down to the beachfront, or by the hotel's private staircase. On your left, a shingle and pebble beach runs to the north for about a kilometer with plenty of possibilities for being on your own. To the right there is a beautiful sandy stretch with several bars and tavernas catering for all tastes and pockets right on the beach. 

DISCOVER CORFU TOWN 
Set on a peninsula and serving as both main port of entry and the commercial center of the island, Corfu Town is home to nearly half the population of Kerkyra. Even visitors staying in outlying areas are likely to pay at least one visit to Corfu Town, as it is a bustling and vibrant city, as well as being rich in historical and scenic attractions. Stroll through the "old city" or the Jewish Quarter, visit both the old and the new fortresses, Mon Repos, the Achillion Palace, the Asian Art Museum, the Archeological Museum and Saint Spirodon Church. There are many fine restaurants and often free theatrical presentations in the National Theatre. Afterwards you can have a drink or a coffee at one of the many cafes on the Liston, where tourists and locals stroll day and evening.

There is public bus every hour to Corfu town from the Agios Gordios village. We also organize car or scooter rental at reception and Corfu town shuttle service

We are a family run business and have been welcoming guests from all over the world since 1985.

whether you come from the port or from the airport we suggest you to contact us by phone to facilitate your access with any up-to-date information

We are at your disposal and the manager of the accommodation but also the offices of the company 24 hours a day for anything you need

At a small distance of 50 m. from the property building there is an ATM, a Mini Market and a bus stop.

In a small distance of 150 m. you can find the famous St. George which is at the south of Corfu.

At a distance of 200 m. there is a motorbike rental and at 300 m. away there is a car rental. We highly suggest our Guests to rent a car instead of using the transportation.

Remember that Southgate is located just 500 m. from the center of Corfu, where there are many Restaurants and traditional Taverns, Bars, Cafeterias, Tourist - Souvenir shops, etc.

The well known Issos, the endless seashore with the unique sand dunes and the crystalline waters is 1km away . 

At the end of Issos you will find the beautiful Korission lake and the lush green forest which both make unique spots for hiking, while the high sand dunes offer excellent sunset views.

In the neighborhood you can walk around all the shops and restaurants are a maximum distance of 10 minutes on foot. You can park your car safely in the private parking of our hotel located directly opposite

The discreet luxury and Venetian style with influences from French and English presence in the island dominates all spaces of Corfu hotel. 
Corfu Secret Boutique Hotel was not only designed to cover the needs of guests or business travelers but to cover a wide range of visitors of the island, those who seek a more personal service that cannot be found in other big hotels in Corfu warmer, more friendly, more familiar. 
The Corfu Secret Hotel is designed for those who love and appreciate art, for dreamers, for those who want to travel for a while to the old romantic bygone eras. 
The friendly and warm environment, the cleanness and the respect of guest wishes aim to change the accommodation into a dream experience. 
Our experience and service make us see the visitor as a customer as someone who is very close to us … Everyone though, without exception, will enjoy the exceptional Greek hospitality, the personal service, the friendly atmosphere, the warm and sincere smiles of our staff but mostly our hotel it's suitable for its cheap prices.

{'access': 'Стильно оформленные номера оснащены кухней с холодильником, микроволновой печью. Также в вашем распоряжении спутниковое телевидение. Апартаменты располагают ухоженным садом с растениями и пальмами, солнечной террасой и бесплатной парковкой. С балконов открывается живописный вид на сельскую местность. Гости могут отдохнуть у бассейна, оснащенного шезлонгами и зонтиками.', 'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'Один из лучших вариантов, выбранных нами в городе Агиос-Гордиос. До пляжа можно дойти всего за 5 минут. Апартаменты Blumarin в деревне. К услугам гостей апартаменты с собственной кухней, террасой и балконом. Расстояние до пляжа Агиос-Гордиос составляет 400 метров. К услугам гостей комплекса номера-студио и апартаменты с собственной кухней, большой открытый бассейн с гидромассажной ванной и отдельный бассейн для детей. Бассейн открыт в период с 1.05-30.10

Семейные Апартаменты (Two-Bedroom Apartment) включают в себя две изолированные спальни,изолированная кухня со всеми нужными кухонными принадлежностями,отдельная ванная комната с душем и необходимым инвентарем.Отдельный вход.Есть возможность размещения одной дополнительной кровати.(доп.плата 10евро) Площадь Апартаментов 45 кв.м

Стильно оформленные номера оснащены кухней с холодильником, микроволновой печью. Также в вашем распоряжении спутниковое телевидение. Апартаменты располагают ухоженным садом с растениями и пальмами, солнечной террасой и бесплатной парковкой. С балконов открывается живописный вид на сельскую местность. Гости могут отдохнуть у бассейна, оснащенного шезлонгами и зонтиками.

Агиос Гордис находится на западном побережье Корфу южнее Глифады. Это туристический поселок с широкой и довольно длинной пляжной полосой с развитой инфраструктурой – тавернами, супермаркетами, кафе, барами. «Изюминка» Агиос Гордиоса в его расположении: пляж лежит в красивейшей бухте, окруженной живописными скалами, поросшими оливковыми деревьями и виноградом. Попав единожды в такой эдемский сад, хочется остаться здесь навсегда. Столь непатриотичное настроение поддерживают предлагаемые в аренду шезлонги, развалившись на которых, кажется, что никакая сила мира не сдвинет тебя с заслуженного кусочка рая. Агиос Гордиос не случайно считается лучшим пляжем на западном побережье Корфу: здесь изумительный нежный и мелкий песок, теплое и очень спокойное море.

Остановка общественного транспорта находится в 100 метрах от отеля, автобусы ходят каждые 30 минут в центр города, столицу острова Керкиру. Так же рядом с отелем есть прокат автомобилей, скутеров, квадроциклов.

whether you come from the port or from the airport we suggest you to contact us by phone to facilitate your access with any up-to-date information

We are at your disposal and the manager of the accommodation but also the offices of the company 24 hours a day for anything you need

At a small distance of 50 m. from the property building there is an ATM, a Mini Market and a bus stop.

In a small distance of 150 m. you can find the famous St. George which is at the south of Corfu.

At a distance of 200 m. there is a motorbike rental and at 300 m. away there is a car rental. We highly suggest our Guests to rent a car instead of using the transportation.

Remember that Southgate is located just 500 m. from the center of Corfu, where there are many Restaurants and traditional Taverns, Bars, Cafeterias, Tourist - Souvenir shops, etc.

The well known Issos, the endless seashore with the unique sand dunes and the crystalline waters is 1km away . 

At the end of Issos you will find the beautiful Korission lake and the lush green forest which both make unique spots for hiking, while the high sand dunes offer excellent sunset views.

In the neighborhood you can walk around all the shops and restaurants are a maximum distance of 10 minutes on foot. You can park your car safely in the private parking of our hotel located directly opposite

sectionedDescription:
{'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'Our Aparthotel consists of 20 self-catering apartments/studios conveniently located 100 meters from the beach of Acharavi and 500 meters from the centre of the resort.  
We offer:
→ Studios for 2 or 3 guests 
→ One-bedroom apartments for 2+2 guests 
→ Two-bedroom apartments for 4 + 1 guests
The accommodation provides a peaceful atmosphere and it has a large pool in the middle of a well-maintained gardens. Optional Breakfast is served
ONLINE PRICE IS FOR ONE 1-BEDROOM APARTMENT FOR 4 GUESTS.

Relaxing family atmosphere just a few meters from the sea, beach-restaurants, bars and the resort centre of Acharavi!

Someone from our team will be available throughout your stay.

Acharavi is the Main town for the North of Corfu.
The resort Acharavi is a busy and lively place boasting something for everyone. It is 35km away from Corfu town (Kerkyra) and around 40km from the airport. Acharavi Corfu holidays are particularly suited to couples and families who are looking for a combination of fun and rest. Acharavi is not just a resort, as there is a post office, bank, a dentist, doctors and all the facilities found in a modern town. It has plenty of Tavernas, restaurants, bars, shops and a superb long sandy beach that, it stays shallow for 50 metres out to sea and stretches the entire length of the town – a whopping 5 kilometres. The surrounding countryside is pretty spectacular, too – one of the world’s best walking trails sits in the hills behind town.
Finally, just in 15 minutes driving, you can find the famous “canale d’ amour” in Sidari village from one side towards Italy and Kassiopi with a picturesque small port from the other side towards the mainland.

500 meters away from a public bus stop.
Lots of parking space

ONLINE LISTED RATES ARE FOR ONE 1-BEDROOM APARTMENT FOR UP TO 4 GUESTS.
1-BEDROOM: (two spaces - one separate bedroom and a sitting room with two sofa beds and kitchen). 

PLEASE CONTACT US FOR SPECIAL PRICES IN MULTIPLE UNIT RESERVETIONS at stamatis at villareginarossa . gr

Free sunbeds on the beach
we organize many activities & island tours, we can also organize airport transfer for our guests, just let us know your arrival details.

Our hotel is situated the hill overlooking the beach  and the Agios Gordios beach is 400 meters way.
Free WIFI  in room, lobby and common areas soon also in rooms .
On the beach section of the hotel we also  have free sunbeds on the beach, we organize island tours, quad safari tours, quad rentals, kayak rentals and many other activities
Room is situated only 5 minutes walk from the beach of Agios Gordioss. The fairy tale location offers breathtaking views of the secluded sandy beach bay. If you are looking to get away on a tranquil holiday surrounded by stunning views this is the place for you!
It has sea view veranda- the perfect place for a good cup of coffee in the morning or to enjoy a peaceful drink during sunset.

If you are looking for a quiet relaxing holiday to get away from everyday life and want to experience Greek Tavern's and cuisine of our village our room is located near everything. We look forward to welcoming you for an unforgettable holiday.

Guest access
-Free sunbeds on the beach in front of our beach restaurant
-Laundry Services Available (on request for 10 Euros per load.)
-Easy Access to the beach
-Easy Access to Corfu Town
- Agios Gordios Village center only 250 meters way

Other things to note
We can also arrange and airport pick-up and/or drop-off at your request

primaryHost: {'id': 2490952, 'firstName': 'Alexis', 'isSuperHost': False, 'hasProfilePic': True, 'smartName': 'Alexis', 'about': 'Throughout the early history of the Jedi Order, the role of an apprentice changed drastically as war and purges forced the rule of the Jedi High Council to bend or become flexible. During and before the Old Sith Wars, Knights and Masters would take on numerous apprentices, training them at their own praxeums or private residences without any direct oversight by a council. Using the term Apprentice to denote their position as a student, many of these students become great Knights and Masters themselves. {'authorType': 'human', 'description': "Α holiday complex of 5,385m2 and is located in the northern part of Corfu Island, in the centre ofAcharavi, one of Corfu’s most popular tourist resorts. Our holiday studios and apartments are conveniently located less than five minutes walk from the beach, shops and restaurants of the village of Acharavi and 38km from the Town of Corfu.
Corfu island is considered one of the prime vacation spots world-wide, attracting thousands of visitors every year and is distinguished by both traditional Greek and European characteristics, which have influenced Corfu's physical appearance and culture as well as the personality of the inhabitants. The island is verdant and has many lovely beaches ideal for swimming and sunbathing, while several areas offer magnificent sunset views.
Our sea side studios and apartments consist of five independent buildings that are either two or three storey high and in total they cover 27% of the total estate surface facilitating the comforts of a stress free and economic holiday in Corfu, providing a home atmosphere away from home. The remaining 73% of the estate surface is covered in vegetation, with lawns and beautifully shaped gardens, ideal for those seeking tranquility and relaxation in one of the prime vacation resorts world-wide, attracting thousands of visitors every year.
Except the ample room, the light and attractive low buildings and the relaxing atmosphere, our sea side studios and apartments in Acharavi also include a snack bar along with a full range of other amenities such as an Olympic size swimming pool, a children’s pool, a pool bar, and other facilities provide the convenience and comfort essential to relaxing in one of the top holiday resorts in Corfu.", 'locale': 'en', 'localizedLanguageName': 'English', 'name': 'Maisonnette - Apartments in Arachav', 'space': "Α holiday complex of 5,385m2 and is located in the northern part of Corfu Island, in the centre ofAcharavi, one of Corfu’s most popular tourist resorts. Οι παραλίες του νησιού βρίσκονται σε κοντινές αποστάσεις γύρω στα δέκα λεπτά!

{'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'Το Villa Makrades 2 βρίσκεται στην Κέρκυρα, στο χωριό Παλαιοκαστρίτσα, και διαθέτει δωρεάν Wi-Fi, κήπο και βεράντα. Απέχει 6χλμ. από την πλησιέστερη παραλία και 3χλμ. από καταστήματα και εστιατόρια

Όλα τα διαμερίσματα έχουν κλιματισμό και καθιστικό με τηλεόραση επίπεδης οθόνης και καναπέδες. Η κουζίνα είναι εξοπλισμένη με φούρνο, ηλεκτρική κουζίνα και φούρνο μικροκυμάτων. Στο μπάνιο υπάρχει ντους ή μπανιέρα.

Κατά την διάρκεια τησ διαμονής τους οι πελάτες θα μπορούν να έχουν την βοήθεια μας σε οτιδήποτε χρειαστούν 24 ώρες την ημέρα. Επίσης θα δαιθέτουν το e-mail και τον αριθμό του τηλεφώνου μας.

Το Villa Makrades είναι 7χλμ. μακριά από το κάστρο της Παλαιοκαστρίτσας και το Μοναστήρι. Το Διεθνές Αεροδρόμιο της Κέρκυρας, η πόλη της Κέρκυρας και το λιμάνι απέχουν 25 χιλιόμετρα.

Η τοποθεσία αρέσει ιδιαίτερα σε ζευγάρια

{'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'With a privileged location overlooking the golden sand of Corfu's Glyfada Beach and open views of the Ionian Sea, Menigos Resort in Corfu Island offers self-catering accommodations with free Wi-fi access.

The villas and apartment have air conditioning, satellite Tv and kitchenette facilities.

With a privileged location overlooking the golden sand of Corfu's Glyfada Beach and open views of the Ionian Sea, Menigos Resort in Corfu Island offers self-catering accommodations with free Wi-fi access.

The villas and apartment have air conditioning, satellite Tv and kitchenette facilities. They also open out to balconies overlooking the Ionian Sea.

Corfu Glyfada Menigos Resort is surrounded by lush gardens and features a restaurant, a bar and a swimming pool. Free private parking is also available.

In Glyfada you will find a number of seafront bars and taverns serving Corfiot cuisine. The hotel is located on the west coast, 9.3 mi from Corfu Town and 11 mi from Ioannis Kapodistrias International Airport.

Corfu Glyfada 73 with 1 bedroom, living room with small kitchenette, equipped with 2 electro-plates, refrigerator and coffee-machine, 1 Sofa beds in the living room, Wc/shower, 1 or 2x air-conditioning, Sat-flat Tv, free Wifi internet access and balcony with nice sea view, parking and share pool.. 
In the resort there is, an independent from us, company, which offers restaurant, bar, mini market and share swimming-pool.
Capacity for 2-4 persons.
New free service: Shopping arrangement, free Wifi internet access.
Bus terminal in about 300 meters away.
Cleaning 3x times a week.

"Corfu, an island off Greece’s northwest coast in the Ionian Sea, is defined by rugged mountains and a resort-studded shoreline. Its cultural heritage reflects years spent under Venetian, French and British rule before it was united with Greece inCorfu Town, flanked by 2 imposing Venetian fortresses, features winding medieval lanes, a French-style arcade and the grand Palace of St. Michael and St. George." from google

Covered parking on site.

{'access': 'Swimming pool, sunbeds, umbrellas, bar, restaurant, lobby, parking', 'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'The apartment has 2 separate spacious bedrooms, separate kitchenette with dining area and a sofa. There is  private bathroom, private furnished balcony plus a patio. 

From your balcony enjoy a view of the sea, of the people passing by and enjoy the sun all day!

Entrance to the apartment can be from the main entrance of the block, or privately from the patio.  

Onsite there is free parking, swimming pool, poolside bar that serves breakfast, lunch & dinner, all day.

This apartment has private bathroom with shower & mirror wash basin, safe box, TV, hair dryer, plug in mosquito repellent, kitchenette, stove top, electric kettle, cookware, dinnerware & utensils, 2 desks with mirror & wardrobes with hangers. Towels, bed-linen, blankets, toilet paper, hand soap are provided. Bedrooms' balcony doors have shutters & smoking is allowed at the balcony & patio.

In each bedroom you will find 2 single beds joined together. 

In the apartment there is 1 air conditioning unit in the living room & a 2nd one in one of the bedrooms.

The balcony is furnished & has view over the mountain, the neighborhood & the sea as on the photo. 

Our extra services include laundry service, iron, plug in adapter & beach towels hire (deposit applicable), printing and wake-up/ alarm calls.

Swimming pool, sunbeds, umbrellas, bar, restaurant, lobby, parking

Happy to interact daily. Also, we respect guests' privacy & we are there only if needed.

The nearest grocery shop is 190 metres far from the apartment & the resort's centre is 500 metres far. The distance to the beautiful beach of Agios Gordios is 650 metres.

In the resort there are plenty of restaurants & taverns, grocery shops & several cafes & bars. Some of them offer sunbeds & umbrellas on the beach.

Agios Gordios beach is quite long  with quite & busier parts.

Free sunbeds & umbrellas are provided in our swimming pool for our guests.

There is the public green/ intercity bus from Corfu town to Agios Gordios. Online search timetable for "green bus B10 from Corfu to Agios Gordios". Timetable changes over the season and you are advised to check regularly. Get off at the terminal and walk 7' to Panorama. To get to the central green bus station either take Corfu city bus No 15 or walk from the airport for about 15'.

Ask us 5 days before your arrival date for possibility of an airport pick-up (surcharge).

We assist with car rental. Prices start from EUR 25/day including 3rd party insurance. Full insurance with excess for EUR 10/ day more. No security deposit required, no credit card, no passport, unlimited kilometers, fuel excluded. Free car delivery and collection anywhere on the island.

The cost of a taxi from Corfu airport or the port is no more than EUR 35. You can ask the driver to turn on the taxi meter or pre-arrange the price. In 00 - 05:00 the tariff almost doubles.

additionalHouseRules:
Check-in is possible 24-hr. Just let us know in advance. 

If the number of arriving guests per room exceeds the number of guests declared upon booking, availability is not guaranteed and charges apply.

Fees apply when existing beds are used to accommodate more guests than room's default capacity, no matter of their age.

Entrance in rooms is allowed to registered guests only.

BBQ not allowed, neither indoor, nor outdoor.

Children not to be left alone or unattended by the pool and other common areas.

Small pets up to 4 kg/ 9 pounds allowed on request at €5/ night. One pet per room. May not be left alone in the room. Pet owner may keep his pet under supervision at all times during their stay and clean up after them.

Guests need to notify in case of damage causing and pay accordingly.

Identity card or passport are required at check-in for registration.

sectionedDescription:
{'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'Διασκεδάστε με όλη την οικογένεια σε αυτόν τον κομψό χώρο. Ευρύχωρο διαμέρισμα  για ευχάριστες διακοπές με την οικογένεια ή την παρέα σας. Μπορούν να προσθεθούν επιπλέον κρεβάτια κατόπιν συνεννόησης.  Θα χαρούμε πολύ να σας φιλοξενήσουμε στο χώρο μας, με την οικοδεσπότη  πάντα στη διάθεση σας!

{'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'Standart apartments located in a wonderful sandy beach in Glyfada . 
Amazing sea view in each apartment .

Apartments Standard type A5 (40qm), with 1 bedroom, living room with small kitchenette, equipped with 2 electro-plates, big refrigerator and coffee-machine, 2 Sofa beds in the living room, Wc/shower, 1 or 2x air-conditioning, Sat-flat Tv, free Wifi internet access and balcony with nice sea view, parking and share pool.. 
In the resort there is, an independent from us, company, which offers restaurant, bar, mini market and share swimming-pool.
Capacity for 2-4 persons.
Bus terminal in about 300 meters away.
Cleaning 3x times a week.
Beach towels: On request

"Corfu, an island off Greece’s northwest coast in the Ionian Sea, is defined by rugged mountains and a resort-studded shoreline. Its cultural heritage reflects years spent under Venetian, French and British rule before it was united with Greece inCorfu Town, flanked by 2 imposing Venetian fortresses, features winding medieval lanes, a French-style arcade and the grand Palace of St. Michael and St. George." from google

Parking lot/garage (free).

City tax 0.5 EUR Per day, to be paid upon check-in.', 'houseRules': 'No pets allowed. Smoking allowed. Events or Parties not allowed. sectionedDescription:
{'authorType': 'human', 'description': "The house is located just out of Sinarades village on the way to Pelekas. Part of the road which leads to the property is private and it's a 3min dirt road drive. The property is located in a very quiet area with no neighbours arround. The house is located In the center of the  property and right next to it is an outdoor garden area and an area that we keep our dogs about 100m away from the house.

Very quiet area, nature walks, outdoor barbeque grill and lounge area.

Contact on departure.

There is a monastery at a distance of 300m. 
Pelekas beach is a 10min drive.
Glyfada beach is a 15min drive.
Agios Gordios beach is a 10min drive. 
Yaliskari beach is a 10min drive or 15min walk. 
Corfu city center is a 20min drive.

Green busses leave from Sinarades village.(10min walk)
Blue busses leave from Pelekas village.(15min walk) 
Both busses go to Corfu city center.", 'interaction': 'Contact on departure.', 'locale': 'en', 'localizedLanguageName': 'English', 'name': 'Green Hill Cottage', 'neighborhoodOverview': 'There is a monastery at a distance of 300m.

{'access': 'Whole house', 'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'Relax on the large balcony admiring spectacular sea views whilst sipping a drink. Watch fishing boats to yachts to cruise ships float by.
Admire the night sky with twinkling lights from land and sea.
If you enjoy a stroll you can walk to Kalami beach famous for the  Durrell White House in under 15 minutes via the goat path. If you’re adventurous you can also walk to Agni beach, Koulora harbour, Chouchoulio beach, Kerasia beach even to San Stefanos! 
Bus stop to Corfu town approx 2 minutes walk.

Traditional Corfiote House with a modern twist!

Whole house

Can keep in touch via What’s app or messenger. I live in UK but I am Corfiote with local knowledge

Bus stop to Corfu town or Kassiopi is two minute walk. 
Parking available outside house.
No car needed as beach is under 15 minutes walk.', 'interaction': 'Can keep in touch via What’s app or messenger. sectionedDescription:
{'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'Situated on a hill with breathtaking sea and mountain views you will find our family run hotel that consists of 42 rooms, all with en-suite bathroom and balcony.  Our restaurant offers you an extensive American buffet breakfast every morning  and our large swimming pool invites you for a refreshing dip or just laze by one of the poolside day beds.  We have free parking and free WI-FI throughout the premises. 
 Dassia beach is only a 6-7 minute walk that offers sunbeds, tavernas and watersports.

Dassia resort has a lot to offer with shops, bars, cafe lounges and tavernas and the beach front has sunbeds with umbrellas and lots of watersports.

You can find car rentals or motor bikes and bicycles to get you around the island.  The local bus runs to the city center every 20 minutes and the bus stop is only 70 meters from the hotel.', 'locale': 'en', 'localizedLanguageName': 'English', 'name': 'Superior double room with panoramic sea views', 'neighborhoodOverview': 'Dassia resort has a lot to offer with shops, bars, cafe lounges and tavernas and the beach front has sunbeds with umbrellas and lots of watersports.', 'summary': 'Situated on a hill with breathtaking sea and mountain views you will find our family run hotel that consists of 42 rooms, all with en-suite bathroom and balcony. {'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'The beautiful environment, the wonderful sea view from your balcony, terrace or garden which is different almost every day and Glyfada sandy beach which is fantastic for small children, not far from anything on island make this spot really unique.

Apartment Comfort\xa0-23 (renovated 40qm on the first floor) 2nd houseline from the beach, with 1 bedroom with Coco mat matress, living room with kitchen equipped with 4x ceramic plates cooker, oven,
big with 2 door-refrigerator, coffee-machine, a Sofa bed in the living room, Wc/shower, full air-conditioning, Sat-flat-tv, Free Wifi, balcony with nice sea view, parking and share pool.
Capacity for 2-4 persons. 
Cleaning 3x times a week.

"Corfu, an island off Greece’s northwest coast in the Ionian Sea, is defined by rugged mountains and a resort-studded shoreline. Its cultural heritage reflects years spent under Venetian, French and British rule before it was united with Greece inCorfu Town, flanked by 2 imposing Venetian fortresses, features winding medieval lanes, a French-style arcade and the grand Palace of St. Michael and St. George. Essentials and ATM shop just 100m and 500m are the restaurants and bars.

whether you come from the port or from the airport we suggest you to contact us by phone to facilitate your access with any up-to-date information

We are at your disposal and the manager of the accommodation but also the offices of the company 24 hours a day for anything you need

At a small distance of 50 m. from the property building there is an ATM, a Mini Market and a bus stop.

In a small distance of 150 m. you can find the famous St. George which is at the south of Corfu.

At a distance of 200 m. there is a motorbike rental and at 300 m. away there is a car rental. We highly suggest our Guests to rent a car instead of using the transportation.

Remember that Southgate is located just 500 m. from the center of Corfu, where there are many Restaurants and traditional Taverns, Bars, Cafeterias, Tourist - Souvenir shops, etc.

The well known Issos, the endless seashore with the unique sand dunes and the crystalline waters is 1km away . 

At the end of Issos you will find the beautiful Korission lake and the lush green forest which both make unique spots for hiking, while the high sand dunes offer excellent sunset views.

In the neighborhood you can walk around all the shops and restaurants are a maximum distance of 10 minutes on foot. You can park your car safely in the private parking of our hotel located directly opposite

All guests can use washing machine in the building for washing clothes. Soap and softener will be provided.', 'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'Villa Pangalis Romantica is one building that consists of five private units, with private parking, private entrances and outdoor swimming pool.
This specific apartment is one of the five apartments in the building and has two spacious bedrooms, one bathroom with bath tab, a huge living & dining room and a wonderful terrace with breathtaking mountain view. All apartments are sharing a large swimming pool with outdoor comfortable sunbeds and umbrellas in a huge garden with beautiful sceneries.

This traditional but modern apartment is renovated and became a lovely family house. The beautiful bar that is located in the center of the house used to be a very old olive mill that processed olives from the residents of Kato Pavliana village back in 1920s. In one of the two bedrooms is still maintained the vinification machine that all locals used to process their grapes in order to produce their homemade wine. Olive oil and wine used to be the most precious goods back in the days. These two processors are maintained in the house with the lovely story while the modern furniture and design give a great fresh twist. Private entrance and a balcony with great mountain views and overlooking the pool, this apartment is perfect for those who are looking for something different!

Guests will be able to park on site around the villa free of charge. Also the swimming pool is shared with the guests that will be staying at the resort and only them. All guests can use washing machine in the building for washing clothes. Soap and softener will be provided.

I am available for my guests anytime and most likely I will be the one to welcome them upon their arrival. I live very near by and will be happy to help with any inconvenience or for any guiding tips.

In 200 meters distance is a new greek taverna with tasty greek food and also with live greek music amd dancing during the weekend. Within very close distances and at a distance of 5 to 6 km, there are well known for their natural beauty organized and free beaches, with water sports and diving facilities such as: The beautiful beach of Agios Gordis. Other beaches are Paramonas, Prasoudi, Skydi, Agios Nikolaos. In the area there is also the lake of Korission with the two endless and unique for the beauty sandy beaches of Isso and Halicouna. Also on the coastline of the area are the cosmopolitan beaches of Glyfada, Kontogyalos, Paleokastritsa, Gialiskari and the unique for her morphological interest beach of Myrtiotissa. There is direct access to areas of historical, tourist and residential interest such as: Achilleion, Pelekas, Benitses, Kato Garounas, Lefkimi, Sinarades, Agios Mattheos. In all the passages of the wider region such as Upper and Lower Pavliana, Pentati, Upper and Lower Garouna, Vouniatades, Aghios Mattheos, which is also the largest urban center of the region, especially during the summer, there is a rich cultural activity with traditional shops as well as Café, restaurant and supermarkets.

Most suitable vehicle for your stay in Villa Pangalis Romantica is a rented car in order to have flexibility in your trasportation for your own independent schedule and for discovering the island. Also a scooter or motorbike will do. Moving around on foot can be tiring because of the hills for everyday needs such as groceries and shopping.
Other options are also taxi and green buss that can drive from corfu town to the villa but are not very flexible options.
Property can assist with car or scooter rentals as well as taxi arrangments

The outdoor pool is available From Mai to Oktober and is shared with other potential guests that will be staying at the resort. Amazing sea view in each apartment .

Apartments Standard type A5 (40qm), with 1 bedroom, living room with small kitchenette, equipped with 2 electro-plates, big refrigerator and coffee-machine, 2 Sofa beds in the living room, Wc/shower, 1 or 2x air-conditioning, Sat-flat Tv, free Wifi internet access and balcony with nice sea view, parking and share pool.. 
In the resort there is, an independent from us, company, which offers restaurant, bar, mini market and share swimming-pool.
Capacity for 2-4 persons.
Bus terminal in about 300 meters away.
Cleaning 3x times a week.
Beach towels: On request

"Corfu, an island off Greece’s northwest coast in the Ionian Sea, is defined by rugged mountains and a resort-studded shoreline. Its cultural heritage reflects years spent under Venetian, French and British rule before it was united with Greece inCorfu Town, flanked by 2 imposing Venetian fortresses, features winding medieval lanes, a French-style arcade and the grand Palace of St. Michael and St. George." from google

{'access': 'From Mid May   to the end of  October our guests have access to the pool next door property swimming pool and to our Jacuzzi from mid May to Mid October , free sunbeds and umbrellas on the beach. 
Our location has many hiking trails. Nearby there are many old villages you can visit and explore and meet the locals and try home made food and local wine.', 'authorType': 'human', 'description': "Sea view cozy  female shared room for  4 to 5 people , with breathtaking sea views , private shower & toilette & sea view balcony.
Located 400 meters from the beach of Agios Gordios and 3 minutes walk from the village center
We offer Free  sunbeds on the beach, free wifi in common areas,we can arrange airport transfers on arrival and departure for our guests.
Activities we organize: 
Kayaking tour, ATV quad safari tour, Corfu town trips, snorkelling, hiking day trips. Join us

ID: O8 / 29 / 6O38

The Pink Palace hotel rooms are beautiful with stunning views of the bay, beach, and surrounded hills. Located 5 minutes walk from Agios Gordios sandy beach. Rooms are  air conditioned, guests have  Free WiFi in the common areas like , lobby, reception area and beach bar.

We also offer Free sun loungers and sunbeds on the beach and on our beach sundeck,  free showers on the beach, free pool size Jacuzzi, access to the adjacent new luxury swimming pool at the nearby hotel, and the Agios Gordios village center is only 3 minutes walk down the hill, where there are many places to go out, shops, tavernas and supermarkets.

Ask and register in the Pink Palace reception for our great activities!

1) DAILY Quad/4 Wheeler island Safaris (weather permitting)
2) Sea Kayak Tour & rentals (weather permitting)
4) Hiking, walking, and trekking (trails to nearby villages of Sinarades, Kato Garouna, Pavliana, and the unique fishing village of Pentati)
5) Horseback riding
6) Tours of Old Corfu Town and the island
7) Day trips to Aqualand Waterpark and other nearby attractions of your choice
8) Day trips to Albania

We also organize private trips to the nearby islands from 4 or more people.

From Mid May   to the end of  October our guests have access to the pool next door property swimming pool and to our Jacuzzi from mid May to Mid October , free sunbeds and umbrellas on the beach. 
Our location has many hiking trails. Nearby there are many old villages you can visit and explore and meet the locals and try home made food and local wine.

Our helpful staff is here to assist you and we also have 24 hour reception and bar.

Agios Gordios is a unique beach location for  quiet, relaxing and fun holidays. You can enjoy beach front restuarants and bars, local taverns, shops, mini markets, long walks along the beach or  through the olive groves enjoying breathtaking sea view.
 you can visit old traditional villages just a short walk way, meet the 
locals, and try homemade wine and Greek food. 
We are only 3 minutes walk to the Agios Gordios village center with shops, taverns, bars, cafes, public bus stop with hourly bus public 
service to Corfu town, doctor, supermarket, etc.

We arrange airport transfers for all our guests for  a small fee. Just call us or email us your arrival details and we will be waiting for you. 

 From April to October There is regular bus service from the Green bus terminal in Corfu town  ( near Lidol supermarket )to Agios Gordios several times a day  from Corfu Town.  You can also rent a scooter, a quad or a car from  the hotel's reception, just ask us.

Our beach is well known for its clean sand and clear waters. We also offer free sunbeds on our private beach for all our guests for the entire stay. If you are staying more then three nights we offer a free night kayak rental for you to explore the nearby beaches and bays. The Corfu Secret Hotel is designed for those who love and appreciate art, for dreamers, for those who want to travel for a while to the old romantic bygone eras. 
The friendly and warm environment, the cleanness and the respect of guest wishes aim to change the accommodation into a dream experience. 
Our experience and service make us see the visitor as a customer as someone who is very close to us … Everyone though, without exception, will enjoy the exceptional Greek hospitality, the personal service, the friendly atmosphere, the warm and sincere smiles of our staff but mostly our hotel it's suitable for its cheap prices.

The Deluxe rooms are located on the highest level of the hotel, offering the finest view of the Ionian Sea and Corfu Town. They are spacious and comfortable, romantic in style, and fully equipped with Free Wi-Fi internet, mini Hi Fi Radio/Mp3/Cd player, complimentary toiletries, climatic control, safe and fridge or mini-bar. 

An extra bed can be added in this room upon request with extra charge.

Panoramic view to all Corfu Island

Electronic door locks

Parking is done on the provincial road in front of the hotel or within walking distance of it.

{'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'This apartment village consists of 15 self-contained studios and apartments with their own fully equipped kitchen and bathroom. There are :
*  studios for 2 guests 
*  apartments with two bedrooms (Max 4 guests)
*  one Maisonette with 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms (max 8 + 2 guests)
The apartment village is on a low hill overlooking the Ionian Sea from every point of it. On walking distance, there are cosy taverns and restaurants as well as bars. 
ONLINE RATES ARE ONLY FOR ONE APARTMENT (4 guests)

The apartment village is spread in two pairs of buildings. One close to the pool and the other on a more private distance.
They are located near Acharavi-Corfu, which is known as Greece’s ‘Emerald Island’.  The apartment village is on a low hill overlooking the Ionian Sea from every point of it. That is a peaceful rural setting, at the start of an oak tree forest surrounded by nature with a fantastic sunset view. Guests are in a private and peaceful environment within walking distance from a virgin, sandy beach with shallow waters. On walking distance again there are also traditional taverns and restaurants as well as bars. And for those seeking something more active, there is Acharavi, the big resort of the area, just 1,5 km away.
 The apartment village offers a strategic position on the northern part of the island from where it is easy to explore the North East up to the North West some of the best destinations and beaches on the island.

24/7

Almiros, one of the most beautiful and virgin areas of Corfu, is situated on the north part of Corfu near the town of Acharavi, at the foot of mount Pantokratoras (914 m.) and just opposite the Albanian mountain range. Almiros Beach is almost 2 km. long and is extended from Acharavi to the picturesque lake “Antinioti”.
The beach has obtained the European Blue Flag. It is a long, beautiful sandy beach, with clear water and unspoiled scenery which remains as it was years ago. Nearby Almiros, there are many beautiful and peaceful bays for people who like swimming on small bays, away from noisy and crowded beaches. Almiros is in no way a resort as there are just six Tavernas servicing good quality food at good prices with very friendly manners.

The apartment village is 800 meters from the beach of Almiros, 100 meters from the Acharavi-Kassiopi main road and 300 from the public bus station. Acharavi is 2 km away.
There is a large parking area.

The family Maisonette is not for rent in July and August, as it is kept for private use. 

LISTED RATES ARE PER UNIT FOR LOFT MAISONETTES WITH 2 BEDROOMS AND 4 GUESTS CAPACITY. sectionedDescription:
{'authorType': 'human', 'description': "Α holiday complex of 5,385m2 and is located in the northern part of Corfu Island, in the centre ofAcharavi, one of Corfu’s most popular tourist resorts. Our holiday studios and apartments are conveniently located less than five minutes walk from the beach, shops and restaurants of the village of Acharavi and 38km from the Town of Corfu.
Corfu island is considered one of the prime vacation spots world-wide, attracting thousands of visitors every year and is distinguished by both traditional Greek and European characteristics, which have influenced Corfu's physical appearance and culture as well as the personality of the inhabitants. The island is verdant and has many lovely beaches ideal for swimming and sunbathing, while several areas offer magnificent sunset views.
Our sea side studios and apartments consist of five independent buildings that are either two or three storey high and in total they cover 27% of the total estate surface facilitating the comforts of a stress free and economic holiday in Corfu, providing a home atmosphere away from home. The remaining 73% of the estate surface is covered in vegetation, with lawns and beautifully shaped gardens, ideal for those seeking tranquility and relaxation in one of the prime vacation resorts world-wide, attracting thousands of visitors every year.
Except the ample room, the light and attractive low buildings and the relaxing atmosphere, our sea side studios and apartments in Acharavi also include a snack bar along with a full range of other amenities such as an Olympic size swimming pool, a children’s pool, a pool bar, and other facilities provide the convenience and comfort essential to relaxing in one of the top holiday resorts in Corfu.", 'locale': 'en', 'localizedLanguageName': 'English', 'name': 'Maisonnette - Apartments in Arachav', 'space': "Α holiday complex of 5,385m2 and is located in the northern part of Corfu Island, in the centre ofAcharavi, one of Corfu’s most popular tourist resorts. Our holiday studios and apartments are conveniently located less than five minutes walk from the beach, shops and restaurants of the village of Acharavi and 38km from the Town of Corfu.
Corfu island is considered one of the prime vacation spots world-wide, attracting thousands of visitors every year and is distinguished by both traditional Greek and European characteristics, which have influenced Corfu's physical appearance and culture as well as the personality of the inhabitants. The island is verdant and has many lovely beaches ideal for swimming and sunbathing, while several areas offer magnificent sunset views.
Our sea side studios and apartments consist of five independent buildings that are either two or three storey high and in total they cover 27% of the total estate surface facilitating the comforts of a stress free and economic holiday in Corfu, providing a home atmosphere away from home. The remaining 73% of the estate surface is covered in vegetation, with lawns and beautifully shaped gardens, ideal for those seeking tranquility and relaxation in one of the prime vacation resorts world-wide, attracting thousands of visitors every year.
Except the ample room, the light and attractive low buildings and the relaxing atmosphere, our sea side studios and apartments in Acharavi also include a snack bar along with a full range of other amenities such as an Olympic size swimming pool, a children’s pool, a pool bar, and other facilities provide the convenience and comfort essential to relaxing in one of the top holiday resorts in Corfu."}

sectionedDescription:
{'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'Ο χώρος μου είναι κοντά σε υπέροχη θέα. Ο χώρος μου είναι κατάλληλος για ζευγάρια, δραστηριότητες για ένα άτομο και οικογένειες (με παιδιά).

Aris and Katerina, the owners of Villa Katerina, will gladly help you with anything you need, whether its a ride to or from the airport, port, bus station by appointment, or whether its simply to give you an occasional ride to the super market if available.

We are located at the begining of the village, on a small hill with a breathtaking view of an olive trees, and the surrounding villages.

Villa Katerina is located far away from the noisy and crowded beaches. We are located 800 meters from Boukari, which is the nearest beach, which is a 2 min car ride, or a 15 min walk, 2.7 km from Petriti, 7 km from Santa Baraba - Marathias, 7 km from Agios Georgios, 7 km from Issos, and 10 km from Halilkounas', 'interaction': 'Aris and Katerina, the owners of Villa Katerina, will gladly help you with anything you need, whether its a ride to or from the airport, port, bus station by appointment, or whether its simply to give you an occasional ride to the super market if available.', 'locale': 'el', 'localizedLanguageName': 'Greek', 'name': 'Villa Katerina', 'neighborhoodOverview': 'We are located at the begining of the village, on a small hill with a breathtaking view of an olive trees, and the surrounding villages.', 'notes': 'Villa Katerina is located far away from the noisy and crowded beaches. We are located 800 meters from Boukari, which is the nearest beach, which is a 2 min car ride, or a 15 min walk, 2.7 km from Petriti, 7 km from Santa Baraba - Marathias, 7 km from Agios Georgios, 7 km from Issos, and 10 km from Halilkounas', 'summary': 'Ο χώρος μου είναι κοντά σε υπέροχη θέα. Гости могут отдохнуть у бассейна, оснащенного шезлонгами и зонтиками.', 'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'Один из лучших вариантов, выбранных нами в городе Агиос-Гордиос. До пляжа можно дойти всего за 5 минут. Апартаменты Blumarin в деревне. К услугам гостей апартаменты с собственной кухней, террасой и балконом. Расстояние до пляжа Агиос-Гордиос составляет 400 метров. К услугам гостей комплекса номера-студио и апартаменты с собственной кухней, большой открытый бассейн с гидромассажной ванной и отдельный бассейн для детей. Бассейн открыт в период с 1.05-30.10

Семейные Апартаменты (Two-Bedroom Apartment) включают в себя две изолированные спальни,изолированная кухня со всеми нужными кухонными принадлежностями,отдельная ванная комната с душем и необходимым инвентарем.Отдельный вход.Есть возможность размещения одной дополнительной кровати.(доп.плата 10евро) Площадь Апартаментов 45 кв.м

Стильно оформленные номера оснащены кухней с холодильником, микроволновой печью. Также в вашем распоряжении спутниковое телевидение. Апартаменты располагают ухоженным садом с растениями и пальмами, солнечной террасой и бесплатной парковкой. С балконов открывается живописный вид на сельскую местность. Гости могут отдохнуть у бассейна, оснащенного шезлонгами и зонтиками.

Агиос Гордис находится на западном побережье Корфу южнее Глифады. Это туристический поселок с широкой и довольно длинной пляжной полосой с развитой инфраструктурой – тавернами, супермаркетами, кафе, барами. «Изюминка» Агиос Гордиоса в его расположении: пляж лежит в красивейшей бухте, окруженной живописными скалами, поросшими оливковыми деревьями и виноградом. Попав единожды в такой эдемский сад, хочется остаться здесь навсегда. Столь непатриотичное настроение поддерживают предлагаемые в аренду шезлонги, развалившись на которых, кажется, что никакая сила мира не сдвинет тебя с заслуженного кусочка рая. Агиос Гордиос не случайно считается лучшим пляжем на западном побережье Корфу: здесь изумительный нежный и мелкий песок, теплое и очень спокойное море.

Остановка общественного транспорта находится в 100 метрах от отеля, автобусы ходят каждые 30 минут в центр города, столицу острова Керкиру. Так же рядом с отелем есть прокат автомобилей, скутеров, квадроциклов.

Также расположена садовая мебель для удобства, где можно обедать всей семьёй на свежем воздухе и делать BBQ!', 'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'Один из лучших вариантов, выбранных нами в городе Агиос-Гордиос. До пляжа можно дойти всего за 5 минут. Апартаменты Blumarin в деревне. К услугам гостей апартаменты с собственной кухней, террасой и балконом. Расстояние до пляжа Агиос-Гордиос составляет 400 метров. К услугам гостей комплекса номера-студио и апартаменты с собственной кухней, большой открытый бассейн с гидромассажной ванной и отдельный бассейн для детей. Бассейн открыт в период с 1.05-30.10

Семейные Апартаменты (Two-Bedroom Apartment) включают в себя две изолированные спальни,изолированная кухня со всеми нужными кухонными принадлежностями,отдельная ванная комната с душем и необходимым инвентарем.Отдельный вход.Есть возможность размещения дополнитель ных кроватей (доп.плата 10евро) Площадь Апартаментов 45 кв.м

Перед апартаментами есть небольшой дворик с собственным входом, где могут играть маленькие дети! Также расположена садовая мебель для удобства, где можно обедать всей семьёй на свежем воздухе и делать BBQ!

Место Agios Gordios  с развитой инфраструктурой. В шаговой доступности находятся множество баров, кафе, ресторанов, таверен, супермаркеты, аренда авто и скутеров, автобусная остановка, пляжные магазинчики.

Парковка бесплатная перед отелем! Добраться можно на такси или автобусом до города, затем сделать пересадку до Agios Gordios.

Влажная уборка производится каждый день. whether you come from the port or from the airport we suggest you to contact us by phone to facilitate your access with any up-to-date information

We are at your disposal and the manager of the accommodation but also the offices of the company 24 hours a day for anything you need

At a small distance of 50 m. from the property building there is an ATM, a Mini Market and a bus stop.

In a small distance of 150 m. you can find the famous St. George which is at the south of Corfu.

At a distance of 200 m. there is a motorbike rental and at 300 m. away there is a car rental. We highly suggest our Guests to rent a car instead of using the transportation.

Remember that Southgate is located just 500 m. from the center of Corfu, where there are many Restaurants and traditional Taverns, Bars, Cafeterias, Tourist - Souvenir shops, etc.

The well known Issos, the endless seashore with the unique sand dunes and the crystalline waters is 1km away . 

At the end of Issos you will find the beautiful Korission lake and the lush green forest which both make unique spots for hiking, while the high sand dunes offer excellent sunset views.

In the neighborhood you can walk around all the shops and restaurants are a maximum distance of 10 minutes on foot. You can park your car safely in the private parking of our hotel located directly opposite

{'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'Το Villa Makrades 2 βρίσκεται στην Κέρκυρα, στο χωριό Παλαιοκαστρίτσα, και διαθέτει δωρεάν Wi-Fi, κήπο και βεράντα. Απέχει 6χλμ. από την πλησιέστερη παραλία και 3χλμ. από καταστήματα και εστιατόρια

Όλα τα διαμερίσματα έχουν κλιματισμό και καθιστικό με τηλεόραση επίπεδης οθόνης και καναπέδες. Η κουζίνα είναι εξοπλισμένη με φούρνο, ηλεκτρική κουζίνα και φούρνο μικροκυμάτων. Στο μπάνιο υπάρχει ντους ή μπανιέρα.

Κατά την διάρκεια τησ διαμονής τους οι πελάτες θα μπορούν να έχουν την βοήθεια μας σε οτιδήποτε χρειαστούν 24 ώρες την ημέρα. Επίσης θα δαιθέτουν το e-mail και τον αριθμό του τηλεφώνου μας.

Το Villa Makrades είναι 7χλμ. μακριά από το κάστρο της Παλαιοκαστρίτσας και το Μοναστήρι. Το Διεθνές Αεροδρόμιο της Κέρκυρας, η πόλη της Κέρκυρας και το λιμάνι απέχουν 25 χιλιόμετρα.

Η τοποθεσία αρέσει ιδιαίτερα σε ζευγάρια

Υπάρχει γραμμή λεωφορείου 3 μέρες την εβδομάδα, προτείνεται η ενοικίαση αυτοκινήτου. whether you come from the port or from the airport we suggest you to contact us by phone to facilitate your access with any up-to-date information

We are at your disposal and the manager of the accommodation but also the offices of the company 24 hours a day for anything you need

At a small distance of 50 m. from the property building there is an ATM, a Mini Market and a bus stop.

In a small distance of 150 m. you can find the famous St. George which is at the south of Corfu.

At a distance of 200 m. there is a motorbike rental and at 300 m. away there is a car rental. We highly suggest our Guests to rent a car instead of using the transportation.

Remember that Southgate is located just 500 m. from the center of Corfu, where there are many Restaurants and traditional Taverns, Bars, Cafeterias, Tourist - Souvenir shops, etc.

The well known Issos, the endless seashore with the unique sand dunes and the crystalline waters is 1km away . 

At the end of Issos you will find the beautiful Korission lake and the lush green forest which both make unique spots for hiking, while the high sand dunes offer excellent sunset views.

In the neighborhood you can walk around all the shops and restaurants are a maximum distance of 10 minutes on foot. You can park your car safely in the private parking of our hotel located directly opposite

{'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'We are looking forward to meeting our guests, offering greek hospitality and memorable holidays
The Golden Keys Apartment is a family run business with a friendly and relaxing atmosphere located in Moraitica village.
Situated on the South East coast of Corfu, approximately 20 minutes from the airport and historic Corfu Town.
The Apartment is 2 minutes waik from the sea, near shops and restaurants and offers ideal accommodation for both families and people of all ages.

Spacious two bedroom apartment with balconies, situated on the first floor, has partial sea view and garden view from two balconies. One bedroom has double bed and the other two single beds. The kitchen is equiped with all neccesary appliances and utensils. The bathroom has all important amenities.

Located in Moraitika, a traditional corfiot village on the southeast coast of the island and only 20 km away from the airport and Corfu Old Town.
By choosing Moraitika as your summer vaccation destination, you have a chance to enjoy warm corfiot hospitality in a traditional village.
Not far from the accommodation you can find supermarkets, pharmacy as well as a bus stop.
A convinient location next to the sandy beach offers various choices of entertainment from the morning till evening, always in combination with greek hospitality.

whether you come from the port or from the airport we suggest you to contact us by phone to facilitate your access with any up-to-date information

We are at your disposal and the manager of the accommodation but also the offices of the company 24 hours a day for anything you need

At a small distance of 50 m. from the property building there is an ATM, a Mini Market and a bus stop.

In a small distance of 150 m. you can find the famous St. George which is at the south of Corfu.

At a distance of 200 m. there is a motorbike rental and at 300 m. away there is a car rental. We highly suggest our Guests to rent a car instead of using the transportation.

Remember that Southgate is located just 500 m. from the center of Corfu, where there are many Restaurants and traditional Taverns, Bars, Cafeterias, Tourist - Souvenir shops, etc.

The well known Issos, the endless seashore with the unique sand dunes and the crystalline waters is 1km away . 

At the end of Issos you will find the beautiful Korission lake and the lush green forest which both make unique spots for hiking, while the high sand dunes offer excellent sunset views.

In the neighborhood you can walk around all the shops and restaurants are a maximum distance of 10 minutes on foot. You can park your car safely in the private parking of our hotel located directly opposite

beautiful secluded sandy beach and bays only 5 minutes walk way.
Free sunbeds on the beach
we organize many activities & island tours, we can also organize airport transfer for our guests, just let us know your arrival details.

Our hotel is situated the hill overlooking the beach  and the Agios Gordios beach is 400 meters way.
Free WIFI  in room, lobby and common areas soon also in rooms .
On the beach section of the hotel we also  have free sunbeds on the beach, we organize island tours, quad safari tours, quad rentals, kayak rentals and many other activities
Room is situated only 5 minutes walk from the beach of Agios Gordioss. The fairy tale location offers breathtaking views of the secluded sandy beach bay. If you are looking to get away on a tranquil holiday surrounded by stunning views this is the place for you!
It has sea view veranda- the perfect place for a good cup of coffee in the morning or to enjoy a peaceful drink during sunset.

If you are looking for a quiet relaxing holiday to get away from everyday life and want to experience Greek Tavern's and cuisine of our village our room is located near everything. We look forward to welcoming you for an unforgettable holiday.

Guest access
-Free sunbeds on the beach in front of our beach restaurant
-Laundry Services Available (on request for 10 Euros per load.)
-Easy Access to the beach
-Easy Access to Corfu Town
- Agios Gordios Village center only 250 meters way

Other things to note
We can also arrange and airport pick-up and/or drop-off at your request

The discreet luxury and Venetian style with influences from French and English presence in the island dominates all spaces of Corfu hotel. 
Corfu Secret Boutique Hotel was not only designed to cover the needs of guests or business travelers but to cover a wide range of visitors of the island, those who seek a more personal service that cannot be found in other big hotels in Corfu warmer, more friendly, more familiar. 
The Corfu Secret Hotel is designed for those who love and appreciate art, for dreamers, for those who want to travel for a while to the old romantic bygone eras. 
The friendly and warm environment, the cleanness and the respect of guest wishes aim to change the accommodation into a dream experience. 
Our experience and service make us see the visitor as a customer as someone who is very close to us … Everyone though, without exception, will enjoy the exceptional Greek hospitality, the personal service, the friendly atmosphere, the warm and sincere smiles of our staff but mostly our hotel it's suitable for its cheap prices. 
You now have the Corfu Secret Boutique Hotel which combines, the warm sun of Greece, the blue sea with the truly beautiful coastlines, and the green mountains. {'access': 'Easy walking access to the beach (650 meters). At about the same distance you can visit the taverns, restaurants and entertainment centers.
Parking is done on the provincial road in front of the hotel or within walking distance of it.', 'authorType': 'human', 'description': "2 separate connected rooms - Total Room Size 32 m²  
2 twin beds  and 1 full bed  
Family rooms are suitable for 2 adults and 1 or 2 children up to 12 years old 
or 3 adults ONLY without children. 
Attention! It is not suitable for people with disabilities because of stairs!

They are located on the lowest level and have a pool view. They consist of 2 separate rooms along a private, small hall which offers privacy and safety for parents and their children.

In your bathroom: 
• Shower
• Free toiletries
• Attached bathroom
• Bathtub or shower
• Towels
• Emergency cord in bathroom

Room Facilities: 
• Balcony or terace
• Pool view
• Telephone
• Satellite channels
• Safe
• Air conditioning
• Heating
• Interconnecting room(s) available
• Tile/Marble floor
• Wardrobe or closet
• Hairdryer
• Minibar
• Refrigerator
• Outdoor furniture
• Wake-up service
• Executive Lounge Access
• Linens

Free Wi-Fi

Smoking: No smoking 

Continental breakfast included

Hotel Facilities & Services:
Panoramic view to all Corfu Island
Quiet location but within easy walking distance of bars, restaurants, etc
Swimming pool and children's pool (depth 50cm), free lounges and umbrellas
Electronic door locks
Bar and pool bar
Extra Continental buffet breakfast
System Clean Water
Generator
All public rooms fully air conditioned
Room Service
Laundry, Dry Cleaning, Ironing Service (with charge)
Free Wi-Fi Internet
Fax / Photocopy and e-mails

sectionedDescription:
{'access': 'The Tria Adelphia Complex is situated close to the main road. The access to our property is easy and by any means of transport. 
Car Rental, bike rental, or bicycles can be also arranged by us. 
Simple make a request.', 'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'Τhe Tria Adelphia Studio Room is for those they seek comfort overlooking the pool area and want to have a relaxing and comfortable holidays enjoying their drink watching the pool area. The room is ideal for holiday makers traveling with family or for couples that want something extra for their holidays.

Surrounded by olive trees, relaxation is at its best. 
The Tria Adelphia complex is ideal for those who seek relaxation, nature getaway and to experience the Greek Hospitality. Our rooms are perfectly equipped for Self Catering needs and our team is ready to assist you to make your holidays memorable. 

Our Rooms face the swimming pool so you can enjoy your afternoon drink at your private balcony, or simply by the bar located next to the swimming pool. 

All of our rooms are equipped with:
*WiFi, free of charge for our guests
*AirCondition System
*Safe Deposit Boxes

Our Cleaning service, visits each room every day, to provide the highest hygiene standards to our clients.

The common areas are inspected and cleaned regularly, providing a stress free experience.

Our Garden will amaze you, as we have plenty of different flowers, to see and smell. 

Our team is ready to support you in every request or highlight you might like during or before your holidays. Always happy to assist you. 

Car Rental is available on site, with competitive rates and an extra 10% discount for our Guests. 

Private Transfers are also scheduled and operated by the team so you do not have to hustle any time. Simply, book your transfer and let us do the work.

The Tria Adelphia Complex is situated close to the main road. The access to our property is easy and by any means of transport. 
Car Rental, bike rental, or bicycles can be also arranged by us. 
Simple make a request.

We are always available 24/7, 7 days a week. Accidents can happen and we are here to help you throughout your stay here at "Tria Adelphia".

The Story and location of Arillas
* The beach of Arillas is officially divided into two parts by a small stream. The North part belongs to Magoulades and the South part to the Afionas Community, which our ancestors used to call “Afionitika”. There is a third part towards to the East that belongs to the community of Kavvadades called “Kavvaditika”.
* Opposite Arillas there is a small island called Gravia.
It is Actually a formation of three islands, Gravia, Sykia and Gyneka. The largest is owned by some goats, that live there and drink sea water. There is a small secret beach there which is called “Amiski”.
* The petrified boat of Odysseus.
If you look far into the North West towards Mathraki island, you will see a small rock that looks like a sail, its name is “Karavi” which means “a boat”. It has taken its name from the mythological story of the petrified boat from Homer’s Odyssey. Odysseus was found stranded outside a bay near a small river by Nausika and her friends. They helped him and took him to the Kingdom of Alkinoos, where he was taken care of and given food, until he was totally recovered. Only then was he asked who he was and where he came from. Odysseus was the first recorded visitor to Kerkyra “Corfu” who was treated with the practice of “Philoxenia”. The art of helping and looking after a stranger.
* In Arillas there are no big resort hotels but only small, local, family owned enterprises, owned by people, most of whom, were born or have grown up in Arillas.

Transportation services.
"Tria Adelphia" provides this service in order for our customers to avoid the unnecessary time and energy they spend at the airport waiting for your alternative mode of transport, as well as the stress and anxiety of finding a fast and safe mode of transport. Our shuttle service can be added as an extra convenience to all your bookings (if you have not already purchased during the booking process) and the guide will be waiting for you at the arrival of the "Tria Adelphia" sign to take you directly to the accommodation your. If you want to buy the transfer service, let us know by making a simple request.

Alternatively,
If you want to explore the island and avoid the extra cost and madness of finding a reliable mode of transportation? Maybe you want to drive to the accommodation yourself discovering the beauty of Corfu? Then you really need to consider car rental service. Guests of the Tria Adelphia earn a 10% discount on your rental.

On the property there are many parking spaces, free Wi-Fi, sunbeds and umbrellas by the pool, bed linen and towels.
Tria Adelphia Accommodation is the perfect accommodation for a relaxing holiday for you and your soul mate or friends. Our fenced private property will offer accommodation and unique moments of tranquility around the pool or under the shade of umbrellas.

sectionedDescription:
{'authorType': 'human', 'description': 'Sea View room @The Pink Palace . 3 bedded shared room in a dream location! The room is equipped with 3 single beds, a private shower and toilette, sea view balcony, air conditioning, fridge, wifi  and a sea view balcony with amazing sea views and best sunsets on the area
a bed in a shared room for 3.
Beautiful secluded sandy beach and bays only 5 minutes walk way
Free sunbeds on the beach
we can organize airport pick up  and many activities & island tours at great prices

The hotel is situated on the hill overlooking the beach and offers air conditioned   sea view rooms en suite 
Free WIFI in all  areas,
On the beach section of the hotel we also have a beach bar and restaurant with  free sunbeds on the beach for our guests.
 shared Room is situated only 5 minutes walk from the beach of Agios Gordios. The fairy tale location offers breathtaking views of the secluded sandy beach bay. If you are looking to get away on a tranquil holiday surrounded by stunning views this is the place for you!

Room has a private bathroom, air-conditioning and WIFI internet. It has sea view veranda- the perfect place for a good cup of coffee in the morning or to enjoy a peaceful drink during sunset.

Schedule our activities according to your preferences!

ACTIVITIES AND EXCURSIONS
1) DAILY Quad/4 Wheeler island Safaris 
2) Sea Kayak Tour & rentals (weather permitting)
4) Hiking, walking, and trekking (trails to nearby villages of Sinarades, Kato Garouna, Pavliana, and the unique fishing village of Pentati)
5) Horseback riding
6) Tours of Old Corfu Town and the island
7) Day trips to Aqualand Waterpark and other nearby attractions of your choice
8) Day trips to Albania
9) Daily trips to Paxos and  antipaxos

discover corfu town which is set on a peninsula  Corfu Town is home to nearly half the population of Kerkyra. Even visitors staying in outlying areas are likely to pay at least one visit to Corfu Town, as it is a bustling and vibrant city, as well as being rich in historical and scenic attractions. Stroll through the "old city" or the Jewish Quarter, visit both the old and the new fortresses, Mon Repos, the Achillion Palace, the Asian Art Museum, the Archeological Museum and Saint Spirodon Church. There are many fine restaurants and often free theatrical presentations in the National Theatre. Afterwards you can have a drink or a coffee at one of the many cafes on the Liston, where tourists and locals stroll day and evening.

There is regular public bus to Corfu town from Agios Gordios , the hotel also organizes transfer to Corfu town and to the airport several times a day, you can also rent bikes or quads at the hotel or a car. we organize daily island tours and quad safaris.', 'locale': 'en', 'localizedLanguageName': 'English', 'name': 'sea view shared room near the beach', 'neighborhoodOverview': 'discover corfu town which is set on a peninsula  Corfu Town is home to nearly half the population of Kerkyra.
